<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When I try to perform Zend_Ldap::search(...)-&gt;toArray(), an exception is thrown:</p>

<p>Message: 0x54 (Decoding error): getting next entry (0x54 (Decoding error))</p>

<p>The actual problem is in Zend_Ldap_Collection_Iterator_Default::next(), which internally calls PHP's ldap_next_entry(). Upon reaching the end of the found entries, which is indicated by returning FALSE by ldap_next_entry(), Zend_Ldap_Collection_Iterator_Default::next() throws the exception instead of returning.</p>

